    "body": "Most distros do have a limit for open files: https://linux.die.net/man/5/limits.conf\r\n\r\nOther clients did have the same problem:\r\nhttps://github.com/paritytech/parity-ethereum/issues/9831\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/16006\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/ethereumj/issues/942\r\n\r\nThis seems to be the solution by go-ethereum: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/tree/master/common/fdlimit",
